  "texts": [
    "A total of 300/800 (37.5%) of the notes underwent dual annotation by two data scientists across four rounds.",
    "After each round, the data scientists and an oncologist performed discussion-based adjudication.",
    "Before adjudication, dually annotated notes had a Krippendorf's alpha agreement of 0.86 and Cohen's Kappa of 0.86 for any SDoH mention categories.",
    "For adverse SDoH mentions, notes had a Krippendorf's alpha agreement of 0.76 and Cohen's Kappa of 0.76.",
    "Detailed agreement metrics are in Supplementary Tables 6 and 7."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}